=Description=

Diogo De Castro Lopes:

"The Gondola Segura is an initiative P2P. Our mission is to encourage fair trade of organic products, ie without pesticides. We want to encourage the purchase of direct conscious consumers. This project involves a platform, an ecosystem of tools that integrates producers, cooperatives, government laboratories to an e-commerce. This portal is query the provenance of products and direct sales. The consumer may invest collaboratively on projects of their supplier."


